<view class="save-page"><view class="save-head"><text class="eyebrow">JOURNEY ARCHIVE</text><text class="title">旅程存档</text><text class="subtitle">在这里接回上一次未完的探索。</text></view><view class="loading" wx:if="{{loading}}">正在整理行囊…</view><view class="notice" wx:elif="{{loadError}}"><text>{{loadError}}</text><text class="retry" data-testid="saves-retry" bindtap="loadSaves">重新加载</text></view><view wx:elif="{{saves.length}}"><view class="save-card" data-testid="save-card" wx:for="{{saves}}" wx:key="slotId"><view class="save-top"><text class="slot">ARCHIVE {{item.slotIndex}}</text><text class="time">{{item.formattedTime}}</text></view><text class="save-story">{{item.storyName}}</text><text class="save-summary">{{item.nodeSummary}}</text><view class="save-bottom"><text>第 {{item.nodeIndex}} 节</text><view><text class="delete" data-testid="save-delete" bindtap="deleteSave" data-id="{{item.slotId}}">删除</text><text class="resume" data-testid="save-resume" bindtap="loadSave" data-nodeid="{{item.nodeId}}" data-storyid="{{item.storyId}}">继续 →</text></view></view></view></view><view class="empty" wx:else><text class="empty-mark">—</text><text>你的行囊还没有存档</text><text>在长剧情中可随时保存探索进度。</text></view></view>
